title: Coastline of Rhode Island, 1976-1983
name: Coastline of Rhode Island, 1976-1983
description: This dataset shows the Coastline of RI and nearby CT and MA including Narragansett Bay its tributaries along with near shore and offshore islands. Reprojected to WGS 1984 using MapWindow and uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.
